name: Beige Sky - Roblox
description:
Check out the original style at userstyles.org
This is a follow-up to a request, I fulfil most, so go ahead and describe the pic you want in the comments or send an imgur link to it. Original image from Newgrounds artist 'unknown' and they deleted the original, an archive link to the original is found in the code. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
